# =============================================================================
# SUNA BIM AGENT — DOKPLOY ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES TEMPLATE
# =============================================================================
# This file lists ALL environment variables that must be configured in the
# Dokploy dashboard under Project → Environment Variables before deploying.
#
# Staging/dev default values are pre-filled where safe.
# Variables marked "REQUIRED — fill in Dokploy dashboard" have no safe default
# and MUST be set by the operator before the first deploy.
#
# How to use:
#   1. Open Dokploy dashboard → your project → Environment Variables
#   2. Copy each variable below and paste its value
#   3. Click Save & Re-deploy
#
# For local testing:
#   make dokploy-setup   # copies this file to .env for docker compose use
# =============================================================================


# =============================================================================
# SUPABASE
# =============================================================================

# Your Supabase project URL (staging instance)
SUPABASE_URL=https://vplbjxijbrgwskgxiukd.supabase.co

# Supabase anonymous (public) key — safe to expose in frontend bundles
